reviewText: Stoked on the limited edition combo set

My son got a kick out of this set. Brave is dear to his heart and he loved there was the horse with it. He'd seen it at WM, but they'd run out by the time I got there to purchase one.  Thanks for having one for me!  It made his birthday (he turned 21).  Never too old for fun, eh?  Arrived in good shape, nothing wrong with toy or DVD or box holding it.  Thanks for the service!
The gift was a hit for my sister! It arrived in perfect condition. The stuffed horse, Angus, is the key reason I bought the package.
